		<time itemprop="dateCreated" datetime="2012-08-07T03:20:04+00:00">August 7, 2012 at 3:20 am</time></a>	</div>

	<div itemprop="text"><p>Ethan, add this line to your comments.php</p>
<pre class="brush: php; title: ; notranslate" title="">&lt;?php wp_list_comments( $args ); ?&gt;</pre>
<p>above this line</p>
<pre class="brush: php; title: ; notranslate" title="">&lt;?php comment_form(); ?&gt;</pre>
<p>now when you click on the comments links the form will appear..</p>
</div>

