	<div itemprop="text"><p>This tutorial sucks&#8230; If you&#8217;re going to take the time to post a tutorial, don&#8217;t &#8220;truncate&#8221; important details that a visitor will need to implement the design technique&#8230; Judging from how many people had to post to try and get clarification on the topic, maybe you should consider revising this so that it makes usable sense.</p>
